caption:
We’re getting ready for another amazing summer at TY in 2025, and need YOU to help us make camp even better!

In addition to the core Tel Yehudah experience, we will also be offering our Merkaz Intensive programs during Second Session. But we need your help deciding which ones (even if you can’t join us for Second Session).

We greatly value your voices so please take a few minutes to fill out this quick survey by October 15 and let us know what new programs would get you excited! Survey link in our bio.
